Merkel Says EU Creating Fiscal ‘Debt Brake’ for All Countries With Euro

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-12-09T04:27:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/merkel-says-eu-creating-fiscal-debt-brake-for-all-countries-with-euro.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  said
the European Union is creating a “new fiscal union” for euro
stability.  “We will create a new fiscal union for the euro that is a
stability union by creating a debt brake for all euro countries
and all countries that want to join up,” she told reporters in
Brussels today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Czuczka in Brussels at 
 aczuczka@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
